Use DCPVerify to verify that your MXF files are valid with respect to declarations in XML files.

Only tested with DCP created by OpenDCP

=========================================================================================================================
RUN THE APPLICATION

Run directly java -jar dcpverify.jar /Directory/For/DCP/Files

Min Java 1.6.
MacOSX ok, Linux & Windows normally ok.

No configuration, no special classpath.

=========================================================================================================================
ABOUT

There is NO GUI (no user interface), and NO interactive mode in command line.

